The time that a vessel is sailing in ECA zones is determined by the speed of the vessel and by the distance sailing in the ECA zones. The fuel consumption of the vessel, using different measures to mitigate the ECA regulations is then determined by the following formula.
1FCVoyage,i=FC+ECA,iFCNONECA,i\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
