				\begin{document}$$ F{C}_{Voyage,i}= FC{}_{ECA,i}+F{C}_{NONECA,i} $$\end{document}

In which FCVoyage,i is the fuel cost for a voyage for vessel type i, while FCECA,i and FCNONECA,i are the fuel costs for a voyage in either ECA zones or non-ECA zones.
